 />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山 齊上齊落</span></span><br />\n老娘對閪眼又濕撚左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11b293f5191ec4348d9e933daa56294abb32a40","tid":1287704,"uid":228195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:39:57.000Z","msg":"雖然睇段文字有猶豫過講呢番說話到底係咪真係50、60後既人所講<br />\n但都一定要正皮俾所有人知。唔好氣餒"},{"pid":"ec993ecd961bec8c1c26ae0a14742ee3c16fedde","tid":1287704,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"睇得 好辛苦，<br />\n<br />\n想死既，打緊仗 唔死得住"},{"pid":"f082674b7745d0fdce59fed11eda684ed6227e57","tid":1287704,"uid":75462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff76f388286fc98added630dcc80a330dc3b2db","tid":1287704,"uid":271641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:56:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嘩！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我冇嘢講。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左粗口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"13462b334952d90ebe65d137fced370be5440bca","tid":1287704,"uid":270866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"我無野講<br />\n<code>好熱血</code>"},{"pid":"60bd8a08f2cf1cf43933fbba8076c4a33ff06d6e","tid":1287704,"uid":53620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:02:36.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"e0cd295ca1f967af298fe0e57c64f36fa306994b","tid":12877